(138,	'Tactical Training (improve AI + etc)',	'COOP resembling Versus\nThe SI AI in this training mode benchmarked some human behavior of versus mode.\nThey judge smarter, dodge faster, and attack more accurately.\nBut they can\'t stop you. Show everyone your tactics.\n\n※ This mode is suitable for 4 players. More than 5 players may cause malfunction.',	'upload/mods/669112c178856/tactr.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/XwTU_Gv6Cn4',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2815665070&searchtext=tactical+training',	'2024-07-12 11:25:53',	18,	4),
(139,	'GIve N Take (share throws)',	'If your teammate misses the items because they haven\'t seen that, but you can pick that up and pass it over.\n1. If you shove the other player while holding a throws, you can leave the throws to the other player.\n\nIf your teammate is incapacitated, you can throw the teammate\'s throwable instead.\n1. If you push an incapacitated teammates, you can bring the teammate\'s throwable. (throws only)\n2. Throw throwables and buy time to save your teammates in the meantime.',	'upload/mods/6691133190409/gnt.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/awtlE3cwOjo',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=251252239',	'2024-07-12 11:27:45',	18,	4),
(140,	'Active Talker',	'This add-on changes survivor characters to actively speak their lines.\n- When another survivor is caught by a special infected, that person\'s name is called.\n- When someone hits by the Boomer\'s vomit, Other survivors call that person\'s name.\n- If everyone gets hit by vomit, they tell them to fight without scattering.\n- When the chargers rush right in front of the survivor, the survivor is surprised.\n- Survivor screams while Charger grabs the survivor and rushes.\n- If 2 or more tanks appear, the survivor will warn team that 2 tanks are coming.\n- When someone provokes the Witch, the Survivors immediately call that person\'s name.\n- When another survivor dies, they call their name and mourn.\n- If the survivor is incapacitated and neglected, that survivor continues to moan in pain.\n- If all survivors survive with the escape vehicle, the survivors rejoice. (You can check it with closed captions)\n- Etc.',	'upload/mods/66911389ad358/atalker.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/YGq7cgCLvR4',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2696358865',	'2024-07-12 11:29:13',	18,	4),
(141,	'Extended Item Carrier Infected',	'Kill and Loot!\nThis addon allows zombies to come out with various items. Like the bile bottle on the CEDA zombies, like the nightstick on the RIOT zombies.\n\n- Police + Pistol (Glock)\n- Riot security + pistol, MP5 smg\n- Medical Staff + Pain Pills, Adrenaline\n- Biker + Magnum Pistol\n- Hunter, Charger + Molotov, Pipe Bomb\n\nFallen Survivor also been renovated. Previously, you only had two throwables, one pain pills, and a first aid kit at most, but now him carry adrenaline, a defibrillator, a combat knife, various rifles, and sometimes heavily armed with an M60 or a grenade launcher, or three throwables. You can even see cases where it spawns out.\n\nThis add-on is fully compatible with extended skin packs.\nAre you using an extended skin packs? So, wasn\'t it disappointing that existing zombie survivors only came out with basic skin items? This add-on applies extended skin packs to items held by Fallen Survivors.',	'upload/mods/669113db7ed39/eici.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/STh1y4N7sgY',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3222172182',	'2024-07-12 11:30:35',	18,	4),
(142,	'Random Infected HP',	'Even infected, there are individual differences.\nNot all infected with Green Flu have the same physical durability. It is realistic that someone are stronger and someone are weaker. This add-on makes individual differences by random adjusting the HP of commons.',	'upload/mods/6691143a265b2/rih.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/F_16LaBbOOk',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3284675086',	'2024-07-12 11:32:10',	18,	4),
(143,	'Junk in Crates',	'No more empty crates!\nThis script fills in the empty crates with junks. Besides, maybe you can get something useful?\n\nFeatures\n- When you destroy a box, junks will be scattered on the ground.\n- Items appear with a low probability of 1-3%. (※ Does not appear in versus mode.)\n',	'upload/mods/6691146aa5293/jic.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/aHTbiKfPoXY',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3239251469',	'2024-07-12 11:32:58',	18,	4),
(144,	'Cursed Cat Menu Icons',	'yes\n',	'upload/mods/669114c7ab1dc/ccmi.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2646790055&searchtext=cat+menu+icons',	'2024-07-12 11:34:31',	18,	5),
(145,	'Jo\'s Animated Menu Icons',	'Just something i wanted to cook up for awhile.\n\nif you\'re wondering why the filesize is a big as it is:\nEach 256x256 VTF was animated natively in 15 FPS with 75 frames,\n\nand turns out each summed up to about 6MB.\nso yeah... i really don\'t know a better compression method ¯\\_(ツ)_/¯',	'upload/mods/66911556ded90/aic.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3213636169&searchtext=cat+menu+icons',	'2024-07-12 11:36:54',	18,	5),
(146,	'Hotline Miami menu icons',	'Icons and logo\n',	'upload/mods/669115a614a5a/hmmi.gif',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2484578401&searchtext=cat+menu+icons',	'2024-07-12 11:38:14',	18,	5),
(147,	'Hotline Miami Background',	'This Add-on changes your background and music menu\n\nHow to Install:\n-Make sure you are subscribed to the mod. Download it by starting up the game and then quit.\n\n-You will need GCFScape to be able to open the .vpk file (C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\SteamApps\\common\\left 4 dead 2\\left4dead2\\addons\\workshop)\n\n-Click on the 2485377489.vpk file to open the file using GCFScape program.\n\n-Extract the l4d2_background01 file to [C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\SteamApps\\common\\left 4 dead 2\\left4dead2\\media] and then replace the old file.\n\n-When you are done, delete the 4 files l4d2_background02, l4d2_background03, l4d2_background04, l4d2_background05, then copy the l4d2_background01 (the mod) 4 times and rename the files l4d2_background02, l4d2_background03, l4d2_background04, l4d2_background05, this will replace the old files you deleted.\n\n-You are now done!\n\nHope you enjoy the add-on!.',	'upload/mods/669115dd63617/hmb.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2485377489',	'2024-07-12 11:39:09',	18,	5),
(148,	'Retrowave Menu Icons',	'Hi!\nThis mod is from a set of mods created by me to give a Retrowave/Synthwave look to the game menu.\nIn this mod, the Icons of the menu, the game lobby and the loading screen are changed.\n\nPlease, if a bug or error is found, notify me in the comments or privately to resolve it as soon as possible.\n(If you can take screenshots of the error/bug it would help a lot.)\n\nThanks for using my mods!',	'upload/mods/66911624a90e6/rwmi.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2113192736&searchtext=menu+icons',	'2024-07-12 11:40:20',	18,	5),
(149,	'Atomic Heart - Terminal Ambient',	'        Replaces regular music tracks in a safe room | Atomic Heart - Terminal Ambient\r\n\r\nFor a louder sound of the track , copy VPK file from ..\\addons\\workshop to the ..\\addons folder .\r\n',	'upload/mods/669116c7b3050/ah.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2943070341&searchtext=atomic+heart+music',	'2024-07-12 11:43:03',	18,	6),
(150,	'Trava u Doma (GeoffreyDayRemix)',	'Replace standart Tank music.\r\n\r\nLink to my magic sound.cache[drive.google.com] if you have problems with music duration.\r\nInstall here: steamapps\\common\\Left 4 Dead 2\\left4dead2\\sound confirming the replacement.\r\n',	'upload/mods/669117270e5bb/tr.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/cUUD36WlIkE',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2937692270&searchtext=trava+u+doma',	'2024-07-12 11:44:39',	18,	6),
(151,	'Brutal Doom Music',	'Hi, this is my first mod ever. I\'m a huge fan of brutal doom, so i made a little mod about the music from the game. The mod replaces the menu, concert, death, saferoom, tank, and credits. This is a metaliezed version of the themes. Note: the sound in the game is much more better than the low quallity video i\'ve uploaded.\n\nThe mod replaces:\nmenu=main brutal doom theme + runnig from evil\nconcert=deep in the code, e1m4, shawn\'s got the shotgun, e1m9\ndeath=e1m8\nsaferoom=intermission\ntank=e1m1\ncredits=mouth of war instrumental by Pantera which is e3m1 in Brutal Doom',	'upload/mods/669117952ce65/bd.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/NXocbFIcXxo',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=210860412&searchtext=doom',	'2024-07-12 11:46:29',	18,	6),
(152,	'Heavy Metal Specials',	'Replaces L4D special infected music cues with heavy metal covers by Xenogenocide. Witch approach cue replaced with retimed version of cue from the Dead Before Dawn addon. Does not replace Spitter, Charger, or Jockey.\n\n*No preview video yet, and in the interest of getting that one Adventure Line replacement for Tank I might break these into each special infected\'s cue. Eventually...',	'upload/mods/669117ce7f516/hms.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=209214767&searchtext=heavy+metal',	'2024-07-12 11:47:26',	18,	6),
(153,	'Immersive Metal Pipe Fall',	'A \"wouldn\'t it be funny if\" that has become a fully-fledged, immersive, subtle, capital F \"Funny\" of its own accord.',	'upload/mods/669118692ca01/metalpipe.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2957114299&searchtext=metal+pipe',	'2024-07-12 11:50:01',	18,	6),
(154,	'Thunderous Metal Pipe Fall',	'I made the promise that if someone asked for a loud version I\'d do it. So IDK, here you go.\n',	'upload/mods/669118a570fc1/tmp.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2957689099&searchtext=metal+pipe',	'2024-07-12 11:51:01',	18,	6),
(155,	'Headshot Feedback Effect',	'This add-on adds SOUND and BLOOD EFFECTS when killing zombies with headshots.\nWhen a bullet hits a zombie\'s head, you want feedback that tells you it\'s a headshot just by hearing the sound?\nThis add-on makes a blunt sound when you kill a zombie with a head-shot, so you can tell the headshot apart just by sound.',	'upload/mods/66911c0d2af83/hsfe.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/TXax983meXM',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2582265366&searchtext=headshot+feedback',	'2024-07-12 12:05:33',	18,	7),
(156,	'SMGs/Pistols Headshot Wound',	'Enables SMGs and Pistols to inflict headshot wound to common infected in any mode like Campaign, Scavenge and Versus\n\n!!! This addon is server-side script. It means this will work only if you host a server and not work if you join any other servers which don\'t have this addon.',	'upload/mods/66911c588f645/headshotwound.gif',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2671600605&searchtext=head+wound',	'2024-07-12 12:06:48',	18,	7),
(157,	'Rainbow Blood',	'Replace the game monotonous dark blood.\nSo that the blood has more rich colors.: )\n',	'upload/mods/66911c9597cc0/rb.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=974949258&searchtext=rainbow+blood',	'2024-07-12 12:07:49',	18,	7),
(158,	'White Blood',	'white Blood .\n\nNot only to modify the blood texture, but also to modify the blood of the particle animation\n\nLike friends remember to evaluate my work,The first time I want to know the latest works, remember to pay attention to my creative Workshop',	'upload/mods/66911ccc16b3d/wblood.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=657857059&searchtext=white+blood',	'2024-07-12 12:08:44',	18,	7),
(159,	'Blood Overhaul',	'This add-on replaces blood splatters, flesh wounds and static blood decals with brand new higher resolution textures. I just figured original textures are kinda outdated since they are 14 years old. Breathe new life into your game with these.',	'upload/mods/66911d5c76536/bo.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1207989591&searchtext=white+blood',	'2024-07-12 12:11:08',	18,	7),
(160,	'Particle Overhual - Blood',	'This mod alters the colors of the blood.\nThe difference isn\'t that large, but some blood particles seemed to be just a tad too bright.\n\nThis item is not authorized for posting on Steam, except under the Steam account named мяFunreal; Steam id \"funreal\"',	'upload/mods/66911d8bd8386/pob.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3019564292&searchtext=white+blood',	'2024-07-12 12:11:55',	18,	7),
(161,	'FPS BOOST',	'What you need to fix the problem when mod dont work on official servers:\r\n\r\n- download this FILE[drive.google.com] and drop to CFG Folder located Steam\\steamapps\\common\\Left 4 Dead 2\\left4dead2;\r\n- created file with CFG extention and named autoexec (just copy any CFG file in this folder, delete all text inside and rename file autoexec);\r\n- paste into autoexec file this alias load \"exec mod\" and save;\r\n- open steam games library, select Left4Dead 2 and open propetries, in launch parameter write +load.',	'upload/mods/66911dd65d37f/fpsb.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2373891426&searchtext=fps',	'2024-07-12 12:13:10',	18,	8),
(162,	'fps boost +fps',	'优化fps\r\n有发射痕迹\r\n有喷漆\r\n修复了贴图高亮\r\n没有天空盒\r\n射击到墙壁上等位置没有弹孔\r\n修复某些地图会闪退的问题\r\n希望对你们有所帮助',	'upload/mods/66911e0395dab/fpsboost.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2911745678&searchtext=fps',	'2024-07-12 12:13:55',	18,	8),
(163,	'Fair FPS Booster',	'Boosts FPS by tweaking graphics settings.\n\nDoes not change main settings, that can be accessed through in-game menu (change them manually). This addon does not remove vomit or give you unfair advantage.\n',	'upload/mods/66912229a5581/FFPSB.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1995550118&searchtext=fps',	'2024-07-12 12:31:37',	18,	8),
(164,	'FPS BOOSTER',	'tested on a laptop with native resolution at 1366x768\n\n\n-Disable the post-processing effect\n-no black and pink textures\n-reduced fog\n-spray enable\n-and more\n-no vac\n\n-my launch parameters :\n\n-lv -novid -nojoy -nomansky -USEALLAVAILABLECORES +cl_interp_ratio 1 +cl_forcepreload 1 +mat_motion_blur_percent_of_screen_max 0\n\n-check compatibility with other addons\n\nextra Funny Jockey Music',	'upload/mods/66912261a98a1/fpb.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2637436471&searchtext=fps',	'2024-07-12 12:32:33',	18,	8),
(165,	'Low End FPS Boost Pack',	'Currently looking into redoing the entire pack so maybe in the next few weeks, months there will be an update if i\'m not getting bored again\n\nProbably the best FPS Boost Pack out there! Thanks to all the Creators for their Mods, please go and support the original Creators you are the best <3.\nImages are outdated but you get the Point.\n\nYou probably really should use this only if your PC is a potato that can\'t run Paint :)\n\nHighy recommended startoptions:\n\n+mat_motion_blur_percent_of_screen_max 0\n+mat_hdr_level 0\n-useallavailablecores\n-lv\n-noipx\n-nohltv\n-high\n-threads (Your number of available threads)\n-vulkan (can improve performance however has buggy Fullscreen, Borderless & windowed only!)\n\nOptional startoptions:\n\n-novid\n-nojoy\n-nosteamcontroller',	'upload/mods/669122a6549d5/fpfp.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2592089744&searchtext=fps',	'2024-07-12 12:33:42',	18,	8),
(166,	'FPS BOOSTER + 30FPS',	'✔️ Optimizaciones:\n\n1️⃣ Eliminación de detalles gráficos: Se quitan pastos y objetos pequeños del suelo y se evitan detalles gráficos a corta distancia.\n\n2️⃣ Iluminación y sombras: Se ajusta la iluminación ambiental, se desactivan sombras dinámicas y la renderización de sombras en textura, y se reduce la calidad de las sombras para mejorar el rendimiento. También se desactivan sombras en objetos y luces del entorno, y se reduce la distancia de renderización de sombras.\n\n3️⃣ Renderizado y detalles: Se limita la distancia de renderizado de los objetos, se manejan los decals (marcas en paredes, sangre, etc.), se habilita la compresión de texturas, se ajusta el nivel de detalle de los modelos a un nivel más bajo, se reducen detalles innecesarios a largas distancias, y se disminuye la cantidad de píxeles en los objetos renderizados. Además, se desactiva la renderización de detalles pequeños en el entorno.\n\n4️⃣ Efectos visuales: Se reduce la cantidad de partículas, se desactiva el efecto de viñeta, se desactiva el efecto de bloom (reduciendo el brillo excesivo), y se desactiva la visualización de la linterna en tercera persona.\n\n5️⃣ Optimización de GPU: Se activa una optimización en la GPU para rechazar píxeles rápidamente.\n\n6️⃣ Otros ajustes: Se habilita la renderización del cielo en 3D y se establece el número máximo de luces dinámicas en cero, desactivando todas las luces dinámicas.',	'upload/mods/669122eb7080e/boost.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3280023573&searchtext=fps',	'2024-07-12 12:34:51',	18,	8),
(167,	'Back to School',	'Back to School is a full featured Left 4 Dead 2 campaign. The storyline doesn\'t interfere with original game and offers completly new setting of Borden city, struggling to survive in an epidemic apocalypse alongside with original 4 heroes. They\'re getting a chance to save themselves, since USA marines are coming in town and not falling back this time. But during the battle apogee something goes terribly wrong and local school - the most safe place in city - turns out to be a death trap.',	'upload/mods/6691237e7e1fd/bts.jpeg',	'https://www.youtube.com/embed/z37koM9hD-g',	'https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=121115793',	'2024-07-12 12:37:18',	18,	9),
(168,	'Diescraper Redux',	'After being firebombed, the survivors must flee their safehouse, and find their way to safety.\n\n\nA 4 map campaign playable in all game modes. Extensively tested on Versus.\nNow playable on offical servers (possibly running outdated versions).\n',	'upload/mods/669123b4e633a/dir.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=121116980&searchtext=',	'2024-07-12 12:38:12',	18,	9),
(169,	'Dark Wood',	'The survivors find themselves trapped on a small stretch of road at the middle of the night. Fleeing from the infected, they have no choice but to plunge into the darkness of the adjacent forest. They will have a long and dangerous journey through the dark woods, creepy caves, abandoned industrial zones, secret laboratory (which must be destroyed), \"Silent Hill\" style deep underground prison, ancient catacombs, and finally face their last battle in the church on a flooded cemetery.',	'upload/mods/669123e90a2b0/dw.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=575682109',	'2024-07-12 12:39:05',	18,	9),
(170,	'Chernobyl',	'The World in Shambles\nThe infection continues to spread all over the Eurasian mainland, leaving its governments in disarray. With no other option in mind, the remaining survivors are heading east to reach the Siberian tundra. As rumor has it, the infection cannot spread effectively in the cold winds of the permafrost region.\n\n\nA Flight gone wrong\nThe four survivors managed to bribe one of the last pilots who is bound to leave Warsaw to fly them eastwards. The safest route seemed to be right over the Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant as they thought there were no people left. Little did they know that prior to the outbreak there were still around 4000 people left to maintain reactor block #1 - #3 and seal off the destroyed reactor block #4.',	'upload/mods/6691243c4d090/chernobyl.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=1646203073',	'2024-07-12 12:40:28',	18,	9),
(171,	'NavFixes',	'More bot friendly nav meshes.\n\nContains a few changes to the nav meshes of\nThe Last Stand chapter 1 (to let the bots press the crane button and not get stuck at the truck)\nThe Parish chapter 4 (bots no longer get stuck trying to jump between the two balconies)\n\nMust be used in order to use the Left 4 Bots 2 automation feature properly.',	'upload/mods/6691248b3720b/navfix.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3226661388&searchtext=fix',	'2024-07-12 12:41:47',	18,	10),
(172,	'Valve Missing Content FIx',	'Adds missing textures and models. These files came in with the first revision of Cold Stream, and the reason they have been removed is because Valve had to remove some content that was unsourced when they released Cold Stream.\n\nThe content was removed after the SteamPipe conversion on July 2nd 2013.',	'upload/mods/669124b612fe2/fix.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=423311431&searchtext=fix',	'2024-07-12 12:42:30',	18,	10),
(173,	'CEDA Vomit Fix',	'blarg - Rochelle\n\nFixes the issue where CEDA infected vomit through their visor. Replaces the vomit animations with 2 unused idles, works online.\nOnly took like 10 years to fix lol\n\nWill not work with mods that alter these models.',	'upload/mods/669124e9e3b41/ceda.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2626267574&searchtext=fix',	'2024-07-12 12:43:21',	18,	10),
(174,	'Hunting Rifle Wrist Fix',	'As of the Last Stand update this mod could be considered obsolete as the hunting rifle was given new animations that fix this issue, but I\'m leaving this up as most people seem to prefer this version.\n\nOriginal description:\n====================\nNOTE: THIS IS *NOT* A REUPLOAD OF THE DELETED MOD BY THEUAREDEAD, THIS IS MY OWN FIX.\n====================\n\nFixes the hunting rifle\'s look poses so it doesn\'t twist your wrist while looking up and down. I tried to make them similar to the other weapons\' look poses so it\'d fit well. In both fully up & fully down positions, the gun remains pointed (mostly) towards the crosshair so it looks natural.',	'upload/mods/66912516f00dc/hrfix.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1431887620&searchtext=fix',	'2024-07-12 12:44:06',	18,	10),
(175,	'Police Riot Zombies ( FIX )',	'Fixed the missing reflections when using the flashlight on the \' POLICE \' text.\nL4D1 Riot version https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2246544888 L4D1 Riot version\nORIGINAL ADDON: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1335429613\nORIGINAL DESCRIPTON BELOW :\nThe riot zombies have now officially joined the police force. Riot zombies no longer say \"SECURITY\" and now say \"POLICE.\"\n\nRequested by Hydra in the comment section in one of my other mods.',	'upload/mods/669125824b9cc/prf.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2248228924&searchtext=fix',	'2024-07-12 12:45:54',	18,	10),
(176,	'Unreachable item spawns fixes (100+)',	'There are few types of unreachable items:\n1. Items outside the map,\n2. Item inside solid (bot can grab sometimes)\n3. Items that can\'t spawn because of badly set item densities in info_map_parameters\n4. Items deleted on map transition because they are too close to starting saferoom\n\nIn total there are about 100+ of these fixed. Most of them in hard rain about 37.',	'upload/mods/669125adb302b/isf.jpeg',	'',	'https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2493132849&searchtext=fix',	'2024-07-12 12:46:37',	18,	10);

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `posts`;
CREATE TABLE `posts` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `title` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `content` text NOT NULL,
  `image` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `user_id` (`user_id`),
  CONSTRAINT `posts_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`user_id`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

